  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "Langua is a suite of language tools that can be used for testing, experimentation, learning, analysis, or creation. There are several main tools: [Gen](#gen), [Morph](#morph), [Deriv](#deriv), [Frequen](#frequen), [Tree](#tree), and [Lex](#lex).",
